---
title: HelloHero: Chicken & Baby Broccoli Korma with Garlic Rice & Yoghurt
description: There’s nothing like a mildly-spiced chicken korma curry for a warming weeknight meal. Let’s add some pops of green with
tender baby broccoli, and make sure to use the fluffy rice to soak up all that delicious curry sauce!
